ABBY: First, we have Brooke.

00:01:51.010 --> 00:01:53.213 line:5%,start
Probation, no solo this week.

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:55.682 line:5%,start
Paige, same thing.

00:01:56.015 --> 00:01:58.985 line:5%,start
BROOKE: I don't think it's fair
