00:38:12.790 --> 00:38:17.061 line:95%,end
Mackenzie won first place,
and she got her first crown.

00:38:17.128 --> 00:38:18.729 line:95%,end
She was so tickled on stage.

00:38:18.796 --> 00:38:20.598 line:95%,end
Maddie was so proud of her.

00:38:20.665 --> 00:38:22.633 line:95%,end
And I just can't wait to hug her.

00:38:22.700 --> 00:38:28.572 line:95%,end
ANNOUNCER: <i>We have the top</i>
<i>Energy Junior Solo, top 10.</i>

00:38:28.639 --> 00:38:31.442 line:95%,end
<i>We have in ninth place, entry number 238,</i>

00:38:31.509 --> 00:38:33.144 line:95%,end
<i>going to...</i>

00:38:33.911 --> 00:38:34.912 line:5%,start
<i>Nia, "Bound."</i>

00:38:34.979 --> 00:38:36.981 line:5%,start
(cheering and applause)

